text: Insano (Nitro Mega) is the tenth studio album by American rapper Kid Cudi. It was released on February 23,2024, by Wicked Awesome Records and Republic Records. It is the sequel to Insano (album) (2024). The album is a double disc, consisting of 27 tracks. == Background == Kid Cudi announced that he would start working on a sequel for Insano in late January 2024, around the week of his birthday.
